<TEXT>
sending us military forces to saudi arabia 
will cost an estimated 300 million to 440 million a month 
defense analysts say and like everybody else the pentagon will 
feel the bite of fuel bills driven up by the crisis in the middle 
east 
higher oil bills could add billions of dollars to pentagon 
spending other analysts say affecting not only troops deployed 
in the persian gulf but us military operations everywhere 
