fred curreys dream greyhound lines inc is 
getting a little frayed around the edges what with a strike by bus 
drivers and others doubts about his company paying its bills 
but the man who led the 1987 leveraged buyout of the bus company 
remains determined 
youre damned right i believe in the system and youre damned 
