lost and the summer is the busiest time of the year 
the objective indicators are that this company has a very 
severe financial problem just operating said the unions putnam 
although he wont provide figures until the reorganization plan 
is ready currey says greyhound is building sufficient cash flow to 
attract new capital 
we are building cash balances gravley said were having 
a good summer things are going pretty well business as usual has 
been our theme song 
